{
  "texts": [
    "There is a slight decrease in 2019, after which the count experiences another exponential surge, culminating in the highest point by 2022.",
    "Keywords were extracted from all the collected publications using the same method as previous research (Cui et al. 2023), in which KeyBERT was used for keyword extraction.",
    "Extracted keywords were compared and merged with the original keywords in the publications.",
    "Subsequently, merging and screening were conducted, excluding terms like \"sentiment analysis,\" \"sentiment classification,\" \"Chinese language,\" and \"Chinese sentiment analysis\", which are used as keywords for publication collection.",
    "A total of 4062 keywords were selected with a word frequency of 6172."
  ]
}